theorem Topology.interior_inter_eq_left_open {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {U B : Set X} (hU_open : IsOpen (U : Set X)) :
    interior ((U ∩ B) : Set X) = U ∩ interior B := by
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  · -- `⊆` direction
    intro x hx
    rcases mem_interior.1 hx with ⟨s, hs_open, hx_s, hs_subset⟩
    -- `x ∈ U`
    have hxU : x ∈ U := (hs_subset hx_s).1
    -- `x ∈ interior B`
    have hx_intB : x ∈ interior B := by
      have h_sub_B : (s : Set X) ⊆ B := by
        intro y hy
        exact (hs_subset hy).2
      exact mem_interior.2 ⟨s, hs_open, hx_s, h_sub_B⟩
    exact And.intro hxU hx_intB
  · -- `⊇` direction
    intro x hx
    rcases hx with ⟨hxU, hx_intB⟩
    rcases mem_interior.1 hx_intB with ⟨t, ht_open, hx_t, ht_subset⟩
    -- Use `t ∩ U` as the witnessing open set
    have hx_mem : x ∈ interior ((U ∩ B) : Set X) := by
      have h_open : IsOpen (t ∩ U : Set X) := ht_open.inter hU_open
      have h_subset : (t ∩ U : Set X) ⊆ U ∩ B := by
        intro y hy
        exact
          And.intro hy.2 (ht_subset hy.1)
      exact
        mem_interior.2 ⟨t ∩ U, h_open, And.intro hx_t hxU, h_subset⟩
    exact hx_mem

theorem Topology.all_P_univ {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] :
    Topology.P1 (X := X) (Set.univ : Set X) ∧
      Topology.P2 (X := X) (Set.univ : Set X) ∧
        Topology.P3 (X := X) (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  exact
    ⟨Topology.P1_univ (X := X), Topology.P2_univ (X := X),
      Topology.P3_univ (X := X)⟩
